<law type="statute"><section id="id499"><amendatorysection chaptername="Livestock" statutenumber="54-171.02"><bookinfo>Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2026</bookinfo><statuteno>54-171.02</statuteno><catchline>Backgrounding lot, defined.</catchline><para>Backgrounding lot means a grow yard that is located within or outside of the brand inspection area and that prepares cattle for entry into a registered feedlot.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 2026, LB1187, &#167; 3. </para><operativedate>July 18, 2026</operativedate></source></law>
